name: Modular Planets #001
description:
Neither down here nor deep away in parallel universes, we all look for that one missing piece. There's a place where all things fit, but just like in our universe, you can't see what's too close to your nose.

Modular Planets is a monthly series of mini audiovisual worlds with a personality of its own.

All audio and visual is made by KinzoisHere.
